skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
WIlderness Dojo, is a continuous innovation paradigm, listen to the latest from the wilderness Dojo Blog, the latest workshops, coding and hardware hacks and more wilderness survival skills.
To start the flash briefing, say "what is my flash briefing", add Wilderness Dojo from the Alexa Skill Store.
Wilderness Dojo can be browsed at https://wildernessdojo.home.blog
It is part of the CoderDojo movement and part of Mutter Gottlich, a workshop series of hardware and software hacks you can build for wilderness survival.
At the culmination of this series, you can spend 14 days in the wild with a robotic observer and test survival with your favorite hacks, please share the media footage of your survival episode with us.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
